      "position": "Fly-Half",
      "nationality": "England",
      "blurb": "England's first-choice 10 through the 10-Test winning run; ice-cold game manager with a stunning 50-22 kicking game and tempo control that underpins Sale's territory-first identity",
      "indexHigh": [
        "kicking",
